'''Community College Leadership and Administration: Theory, Practice, and Change''' (2010) is a [[College]] and [[Academic administration|University Administration]] textbook by Dr. [[J. Luke Wood|J Luke Wood]] and published by [[Peter Lang (publisher)|Peter Lange]].

== Reception ==
The textbook was a top 10 seller on [[Barnes & Noble|Barnes and Nobles]] in the category of College and University Administration (currently ranked #7). The book also recently ranked #6 in [[Economics|Economic Theory]] this year on [[Amazon.com|Amazon]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://interwork.sdsu.edu/sp/m2c3/2014/05/24/bookrankings/|title=Dr. J. Luke Wood’s book reaches important Amazon.com milestone|date=2014-05-24|website=M2C3|language=en-US|access-date=2016-06-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630020909/http://interwork.sdsu.edu/sp/m2c3/2014/05/24/bookrankings/|archivedate=2016-06-30|df=}}</ref>

